01:01:03.000 --> 01:01:04.360 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Chociaż...

01:01:04.679 --> 01:01:09.519 line:85% position:50% size:80%
SZELEST DRUKOWANYCH KARTEK

01:01:09.719 --> 01:01:12.239 line:85% position:50% size:80%
