Siostro?

01:14:55.960 --> 01:14:57.640 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Czy tu był ktoś?

01:14:57.720 --> 01:14:59.720 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Gdzie?

01:15:00.520 --> 01:15:02.520 line:85% position:50% size:80%
